gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Trail Blazers 109, Suns 104
gameRecap.excerpt: Despite Kevin Durant’s 40 points (16-28 FG) and five assists, the Suns fall to the Trail Blazers, 109-104. Anfernee Simons (23 points, seven assists) and Jerami Grant (22 points, four assists) combine for 47 points for the Trail Blazers in the victory. The Trail Blazers snap a 7-game losing streak and improve to 7-19 on the season, while the Suns fall to 14-13.
